ORG 0x1BE
STRING: WORD 0x561
POINTER: WORD ?
STOP: WORD 0x0D

START: CLA
LD STRING
ST POINTER

S1: IN 0x03
AND #0x40
BEQ S1
LD (POINTER)
SWAB
OUT 0x02

SXTB
CMP STOP
BEQ FINISH

S2: IN 0x03
AND #0x40
BEQ S2
LD (POINTER)+

OUT 0x02

SXTB
CMP STOP
BEQ FINISH

JUMP S1
FINISH: HLT

